# Add 'Korean Revised Version' (HR2) Support

This plan outlines the steps to add support for the "Korean Revised Version" (NKRV/HR2) to the Bible application.

## User Review Required

> [!IMPORTANT]
> **Missing Data Source**: Genuine "NKRV" (Gaeyeok Gaejeong) JSON data is copyrighted and not freely available online.
> **Action Required**: I will create a placeholder file `public/data/ko_hr2.json` by copying the existing [ko_krv.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/public/data/ko_krv.json). The application will *function* with HR2 selected, but the *text* will be identical to KRV until you replace `ko_hr2.json` with the actual NKRV data file.

## Proposed Changes

### Data
#### [NEW] [ko_hr2.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/public/data/ko_hr2.json)
- Create as a copy of [ko_krv.json](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/public/data/ko_krv.json) to serve as a placeholder.

### Services
#### [MODIFY] [BibleService.js](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/services/BibleService.js)
- Update [loadBibleData](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/services/BibleService.js#85-105) to handle 'HR2' version and load `ko_hr2.json`.

### UI
#### [MODIFY] [BiblePage.jsx](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/pages/BiblePage.jsx)
- Add "HR2" (한글개역개정) to the version selection buttons.
- Ensure logic correctly passes 'HR2' to [BibleService](file:///c:/Users/admin/.gemini/%EB%82%98%EC%9D%98%20%EC%82%AC%EB%9E%91%ED%95%98%EB%8A%94%20%EC%B1%85/src/services/BibleService.js#70-121).

## Verification Plan

### Manual Verification
1.  **Launch App**: Open the application in the browser.
2.  **Navigate to Bible**: Go to the Bible page.
3.  **Check UI**: Verify that a new button "HR2" (or "개역개정") is visible.
4.  **Select Version**: Click the "HR2" button.
5.  **Verify Load**: Ensure Bible text loads without errors. (Note: Text will be KRV for now).
